Marco Reus completed a hat-trick against Galatasaray on Tuesday night, despite scoring only once.

The Borussia Dortmund star scored his side's first goal in the 4-1 win at the Westfalenstadion, and celebrated by covering his mouth with his hand.

For iPhone users who may have kept an eye on the 25-year-old's form in recent weeks, the celebration completed a trio of emoji references.

