The three popular symbols - a symbol of a monkey covering his eyes, ears and mouth - have been Reus' celebration for his last three goals.

Reus covered his ears on Saturday for his goal against Bayern Munich, covered his eyes for the strike against St Pauli last week and completed the hat-trick on Tuesday.

The symbols, a play on the phrase 'hear no evil, see no evil, speak no evil' are among the most popular emojis used on the iPhone.

